    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I think this is related to our node logger, not to the compilation pipeline. The problem is that we use that special character to update the \"current\" line. We should do that only when stdout is not a tty.\r\n\r\nFWIW: the solc CLI seems to handle this correctly as far as I can tell",
